name: CH&A global group
description:
CH&A is a global strategic partner that connects organizations with elite marketing minds and custom-tailored solutions—trusted by industry giants for over 25 years.
 We strive to enable our clients to achieve their marketing objectives and elevate their market presence through innovative strategies and tailored plans.
With a legacy built on results, CH&A delivers transformative marketing strategies led by seasoned CMOs and industry visionaries. Our mission is simple: to help your business grow, lead, and win.

✔ Over 50 major brands served
✔ Multinational expertise
✔ Customized, results-driven plans

 Over the years, CH&A has worked with more than 50 prestigious companies, including a Nobel prize Winner, and established itself as a trusted partner for marketing success. Some of our notable clients include:
Colgate-Palmolive, The Coca-Cola Company, Gruma Corporation, Firestone, Polymer, Direct TV, Chiquita Brands, Hi-C, Adidas Group, JanSport, ANC (National—Alamo Rent a car), INS, Componentes El Orbe, Kölbi, Costa Rican National Soccer Federation, Abre Group, Roblealto Foundation, GKH Group, Villamagna Group, Dipo Group.
